gba(0, 128, 128, 0.3), rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3)), url('../../files/img/training/HCA_Single_Cell_Omics_in_person_Computational_and_Experimental_Design_Workshop/HSCOpCEDW_16.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mySlides fade\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3), rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3)), url('../../files/img/training/HCA_Single_Cell_Omics_in_person_Computational_and_Experimental_Design_Workshop/HSCOpCEDW_16.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mySlides fade\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3), rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3)), url('../../files/img/training/HCA_Single_Cell_Omics_in_person_Computational_and_Experimental_Design_Workshop/HSCOpCEDW_17.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mySlides fade\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3), rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3)), url('../../files/img/training/HCA_Single_Cell_Omics_in_person_Computational_and_Experimental_Design_Workshop/HSCOpCEDW_18.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mySlides fade\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3), rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3)), url('../../files/img/training/HCA_Single_Cell_Omics_in_person_Computational_and_Experimental_Design_Workshop/HSCOpCEDW_19.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mySlides fade\" style=\"background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom right, rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3), rgba(0, 128, 128, 0.3)), url('../../files/img/training/HCA_Single_Cell_Omics_in_person_Computational_and_Experimental_Design_Workshop/HSCOpCEDW_20.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;\"></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Text Overlay on the Background Image -->\n  <div style=\"position: absolute; bottom: 40px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); text-align: center; width: 100%;\">\n    <h1 style=\"font-size: 3em; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\">HCA Thailand 2024 Workshop</h1>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 1.5em; text-align: center; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;\">Hands-on computational and experimental design workshop on single-cell sequencing technologies, bioinformatics, and omics integration.</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Workshop Details Section -->\n<section id=\"workshop-details\" style=\"padding: 40px 20px; text-align: center;\">\n  <h2>About the Workshop</h2>\n  <p>Single-cell sequencing technologies are powerful tools used to assess genomic, transcriptomic, and proteomic information at the single-cell level. \n  In recent years, the application of techniques that use single-cell sequencing has become increasingly common in several areas of research: including medicine, \n  agriculture, and other life sciences disciplines. The workshop focuses on providing hands-on experience and in-depth bioinformatics training to ensure participants \n  gain a strong foundation in single-cell methodologies.</p>\n\n  <h3>Learning Outcomes</h3>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: none; padding: 0; text-align: central; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n    <li><strong>Module 1:</strong> Preprocessing of raw scRNA-seq data using various methods (10X Genomics, CEL-seq2, etc.).</li>\n    <li><strong>Module 2:</strong> Quality control, exploratory analysis, normalization, clustering, and differential expression analysis.</li>\n    <li><strong>Module 3:</strong> Data integration and batch-effect correction using Seurat and Harmony.</li>\n    <li><strong>Module 4:</strong> Deciphering cell-cell communication using LIANA.</li>\n    <li><strong>Module 5:</strong> BCR/TCR profiling and CITE-Seq in single-cell analysis.</li>\n    <li><strong>Module 6:</strong> Trajectory inference and pseudotemporal ordering using Monocle3.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <h3>Funding and Collaborators</h3>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: none; padding: 0; text-align: central; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n    <li>Shalek Lab - MIT, Harvard Stem Cell Institute, and Mahidol University.</li>\n    <li>Supported by the Human Cell Atlas and Wellcome Connecting Science.</li>\n    <li>Collaborators include:</li>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Nuo \"Ivy\" Liu, MIT/Broad Institute/Ragon Institute, US</li>\n      <li>Sergio Triana, MIT/Broad Institute/Ragon Institute, US</li>\n      <li>Son Ngoc Nguyen, MIT/Broad Institute/Ragon Institute, US</li>\n      <li>Constantine N Tzouanas, MIT/Broad Institute/Ragon Institute, US</li>\n    </ul>\n  </ul>\n\n\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: bold;\">Acknowledgements</h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2em;\">\n    <img src=\"../../files/img/training/HCA_Single_Cell_Omics_in_person_Computational_and_Experimental_Design_Workshop/shalek_lab.png\" alt=\"Shalek Lab Partner\" style=\"max-width: 2000px; margin: 10px;\">\n    <img src=\"../../files/img/training/HCA_Single_Cell_Omics_in_person_Computational_and_Experimental_Design_Workshop/Wellcome_Connecting_Science.png\" alt=\"Wellcome Connecting Science Partner\" style=\"max-width: 200px; margin: 10px;\">\n    <img src=\"../../files/img/training/HCA_Single_Cell_Omics_in_person_Computational_and_Experimental_Design_Workshop/human_cell_atlas.png\" alt=\"human cell atlas  Partner\" style=\"max-width: 160px; margin: 10px;\">\n    \n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: bold;\">Founding & Hosting</h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2em;\">\n    <img src=\"../../files/img/training/HCA_Single_Cell_Omics_in_person_Computational_and_Experimental_Design_Workshop/czi.jpg\" alt=\"czi Partner\" style=\"max-width: 150px; margin: 10px;\">\n    <img src=\"../../files/img//training/HCA_Single_Cell_Omics_in_person_Computational_and_Experimental_Design_Workshop/mahidol_university.png\" lt=\"Mahidol University Partner\" style=\"max-width: 150px; margin: 10px;\">\n  <h3 style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: bold;\">Donating kits</h3>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 2em;\">\n    <img src=\"../../files/img/training/HCA_Single_Cell_Omics_in_person_Computational_and_Experimental_Design_Workshop/10x_genomics.png\" alt=\"10x_genomics Partner\" style=\"max-width: 100px; margin: 10px;\">\n    <img src=\"../../files/img/training/HCA_Single_Cell_Omics_in_person_Computational_and_Experimental_Design_Workshop/parsebio.png\" alt=\"10x_genomics Partner\" style=\"max-width: 150px; margin: 10px;\">\n\n\n\n\n<!-- Workshop Dates and Location Section (moved to the bottom) -->\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center; font-weight: bold;\">Location and Schedule</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; font-size: 1em;\">\n  <p>Mahidol University, Bangkok, Thailand</p>\n  <p>24th - 28th June, 2024</p>\n\n</section>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<a href=\"https://events.humancellatlas.org/hca_asiaws2024/home\" class=\"btn btn-primary rounded-pill me-2\">More Details</a>\n`);\n</script>\n\n<!-- Slideshow CSS and General Styles -->\n<style>\n  /* Slideshow container */\n  .slideshow-container {\n    position: relative;\n    height: 100vh;\n    width: 100%;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n\n  /* Each slide */\n  .mySlides {\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    background-size: cover;\n    background-position: center;\n    opacity: 0;\n    transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out;\n  }\n\n  /* Make the first slide visible initially */\n  .mySlides:first-child {\n    opacity: 1;\n  }\n\n  section#workshop-details {\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n    color: #333;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    background-color: #f9f9f9;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n  }\n\n  /* Heading styling for consistency */\n  h1, h2, h3 {\n    margin-top: 20px;\n    margin-bottom: 10px;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    text-align: center; /* Center the headings */\n  }\n  /* Specific class for description */\n  .description {\n    text-align: cen